{
  "skill_id": "avoid-ai-formulations",
  "version": "1.0",
  "cases": [
    {
      "id": "case_1",
      "input": {
        "text": "Revidiraj ovaj sažetak eliminirajući AI formulacije. Zadržaj medicinsku točnost i akademski ton.\n\"This study aims to delve into the effectiveness of high-flow nasal cannula therapy. It is worth noting that HFNC has gained significant traction in recent years. Furthermore, our findings underscore the importance of early intervention. In conclusion, HFNC represents a promising approach that warrants further investigation.\""
      },
      "assertions": [
        {
          "type": "not_contains",
          "value": "delve",
          "description": "not_contains: delve"
        },
        {
          "type": "not_contains",
          "value": "It is worth noting",
          "description": "not_contains: It is worth noting"
        },
        {
          "type": "not_contains",
          "value": "underscore",
          "description": "not_contains: underscore"
        },
        {
          "type": "not_contains",
          "value": "warrants further investigation",
          "description": "not_contains: warrants further investigation"
        },
        {
          "type": "not_contains",
          "value": "In conclusion",
          "description": "not_contains: In conclusion"
        },
        {
          "type": "contains",
          "value": "HFNC",
          "description": "termin ostaje"
        },
        {
          "type": "last_sentence_not_question",
          "description": "Last sentence not ?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "case_2",
      "input": {
        "text": "Daj mi konkretne strategije i listu fraza koje treba izbjegavati pri pisanju uvoda medicinskog članka, s konkretnim alternativama za svaku zabranjenu frazu."
      },
      "assertions": [
        {
          "type": "regex_match",
          "value": "delve|worth noting|underscore|pave the way|navigate",
          "description": "navedeni kao primjeri koje treba izbjegavati"
        },
        {
          "type": "regex_match",
          "value": "umjesto|instead|zamijeni|replace|alternativ",
          "description": "regex_match: umjesto|instead|zamijeni|replace|alternativ"
        },
        {
          "type": "contains",
          "value": "aktivan glagol",
          "description": "contains: aktivan glagol"
        },
        {
          "type": "contains",
          "value": "active verb",
          "description": "contains: active verb"
        },
        {
          "type": "regex_match",
          "value": "aktivn.{0,50}glagol",
          "description": "strategija"
        },
        {
          "type": "not_contains",
          "value": "nije moguće",
          "description": "not_contains: nije moguće"
        },
        {
          "type": "word_count_below",
          "value": 600,
          "description": "word_count_below: 600"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "case_3",
      "input": {
        "text": "Revidiraj diskusiju, ukloni AI fraze, ali NE briši standardne akademske izraze kao \"statistically significant\", \"95% confidence interval\" ili \"p-value\". Razlikuj AI fraze od legitimne terminologije.\n\"These groundbreaking results certainly demonstrate that, importantly, our intervention paves the way for future research. The data shows a statistically significant reduction (p=0.02, 95% CI 0.45–0.89) in 30-day mortality.\""
      },
      "assertions": [
        {
          "type": "not_contains",
          "value": "groundbreaking",
          "description": "not_contains: groundbreaking"
        },
        {
          "type": "not_contains",
          "value": "certainly",
          "description": "not_contains: certainly"
        },
        {
          "type": "not_contains",
          "value": "paves the way",
          "description": "not_contains: paves the way"
        },
        {
          "type": "contains",
          "value": "statistically significant",
          "description": "legitimni termin ostaje"
        },
        {
          "type": "regex_match",
          "value": "(?i)(95%\\ CI|confidence\\ interval)",
          "description": "contains: 95% CI OR ostaje"
        },
        {
          "type": "contains",
          "value": "p=0.02",
          "description": "numerički podaci ostaju"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "case_significance_inflation",
      "input": {
        "text": "Revidiraj bez gubitka činjenica:\n\"The opening of the new ICU unit marked a pivotal moment in regional care and stands as a testament to the hospital's enduring legacy.\""
      },
      "assertions": [
        {
          "type": "not_contains",
          "value": "pivotal moment",
          "description": "not_contains: pivotal moment"
        },
        {
          "type": "not_contains",
          "value": "stands as a testament",
          "description": "not_contains: stands as a testament"
        },
        {
          "type": "not_contains",
          "value": "enduring legacy",
          "description": "not_contains: enduring legacy"
        },
        {
          "type": "contains",
          "value": "ICU",
          "description": "topic preserved"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "case_copula_avoidance",
      "input": {
        "text": "Zamijeni copula avoidance običnim glagolima:\n\"The clinic boasts a modern laboratory and serves as a regional referral center for ECMO.\""
      },
      "assertions": [
        {
          "type": "not_contains",
          "value": "boasts",
          "description": "not_contains: boasts"
        },
        {
          "type": "not_contains",
          "value": "serves as",
          "description": "not_contains: serves as"
        },
        {
          "type": "regex_match",
          "value": "(?i)ECMO|laborator",
          "description": "facts preserved"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}